# LAMMPS INPUT SCRIPT
# Find minimum energy fcc ( face-centered cubic ) atomic configuration
# Mark Tschopp
# Syntax, lmp_exe < calc_fcc.in

###############################
# INITIALIZATION
clear
units metal
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic
atom_modify map array


###############################
# Atom definition
lattice fcc ${latconst} orient x 1 0 0 orient y 0 1 0 orient z 0 0 1
lattice fcc 4.30 orient x 1 0 0 orient y 0 1 0 orient z 0 0 1
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 4.3 4.3 4.3
region box block 0 1 0 1 0 1 units lattice
create_box 1 box
